---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/navbar.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import profileImg from "../images/me-architect.jpg";
import labImg from "../images/bass-lab.webp";
import fatherhoodImg from "../images/fatherhood.webp";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <Navbar />
  <div class="pt-20 md:pt-24 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <header class="relative text-left py-16 md:py-20">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/65 backdrop-blur-2xl border-b border-violet-100/50"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
          <p
            class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-indigo-700/90 mb-4"
          >
            Systems of the Heart, Sound &amp; Code
          </p>
          <h1
            class="text-[2.4rem] md:text-[3.1rem] leading-tight font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 drop-shadow-sm"
          >
            JoySomatic
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/85 max-w-none">
            Decoding the language of the Body, Relationships, and Systems
            through somatics, sound, and engineering.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="pb-16">
        <section id="about" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
          <h2
            class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1"
          >
            Hi, I’m José.
          </h2>

          <div
            class="mt-8 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90 leading-relaxed"
          >
            <div
              class="md:float-right md:ml-10 mb-8 w-full md:w-72 lg:w-80 aspect-square relative group"
            >
              <div
                class="absolute -inset-1.5 bg-gradient-to-tr from-pink-200 to-violet-300 rounded-3xl blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-700"
              >
              </div>

              <div
                class="relative h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/40 shadow-xl"
              >
                <Image
                  src={profileImg}
                  alt="José Oñate"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="mb-6">
              Born in 1982, my journey into healing began as a teenager, driven
              by the weight of intense anxiety. I later realized I was a Highly
              Sensitive child, born with a deep empathy and intuition that I’ve
              spent the last two decades learning to navigate through therapy,
              somatic practices, and lived experience.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-6">
              Since 2022, I have navigated the rhythms of co-parenting. This
              journey of humility has been my greatest teacher in presence and
              nervous system regulation. Now, as I enter this next chapter, I am
              re-activating my roots as a Developer and Sound Engineer.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-6">
              After a significant hiatus to focus on family, I am back at the
              keyboard and in the studio. I am currently "building in public,"
              documenting my return to code and audio engineering as I merge
              these technical worlds with my somatic coaching practice.
            </p>

            <blockquote
              class="border-l-4 border-pink-200 pl-4 italic text-indigo-900/85 mb-8"
            >
              "I am currently re-coding my life and my tools. I look at life
              through two lenses: the Somatic heart that feels the rhythm, and
              the Engineer’s mind that understands the system. I’m finding the
              signal in the noise, one line of code at a time."
            </blockquote>

            <div class="clear-both"></div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="relationships" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
          <h2
            class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1"
          >
            Relationship &amp; Somatic Coaching
          </h2>

          <p class="mt-6 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90">
            My primary energy is dedicated to helping people navigate the
            complexities of human connection. I help individuals and couples
            "debug" the patterns that keep them stuck, using the body as our
            primary source of truth.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
            <div
              class="rounded-[2.25rem] bg-white/90 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(148,163,184,0.5)] px-5 py-5"
            >
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-950/90">
                Relational Insight
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2.5 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/85">
                We look at the <strong>System</strong> of your relationship. I help
                you identify the "phase cancellation" in your communication—the moments
                where you clash instead of harmonize—and help you rewrite those scripts
                for deeper connection.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="rounded-[2.25rem] bg-white/90 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(148,163,184,0.5)] px-5 py-5"
            >
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-950/90">
                In-Person Sessions (Safe Spaces)
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2.5 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/85">
                I believe healing happens best where you feel most grounded.
                In-person sessions can be held in <strong
                  >nature, a private home, or any quiet space</strong
                > that feels safe and supportive for you. Removing the clinical office
                environment allows the nervous system to open in its own time.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="rounded-[2.25rem] bg-white/90 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(148,163,184,0.5)] px-5 py-5"
            >
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-950/90">
                Remote &amp; Async Coaching (Available to All)
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2.5 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/85">
                Presence isn't limited by geography. I offer
                <strong>Virtual Meetings (Google Meet)</strong> and
                <strong>Asynchronous Voice Coaching</strong> for everyone—whether
                you are across the world or just prefer to process your growth from
                the comfort of your own space.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="lab" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
          <h2
            class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1"
          >
            The JoySomatic Lab: Building in Public
          </h2>

          <div class="mt-8">
            <div
              class="float-right ml-4 md:ml-10 mb-4 w-32 h-32 md:w-56 md:h-56 relative group"
            >
              <div
                class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-tr from-emerald-200/40 to-sky-300/40 rounded-2xl blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-700"
              >
              </div>

              <div
                class="relative h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/40 shadow-lg"
              >
                <Image
                  src={labImg}
                  alt="The Bass Studio Lab"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <ul
              class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90"
            >
              <li>
                <strong>The Journey Back:</strong> You can follow my progress on <strong
                  >GitHub</strong
                >
                as I refresh my Python skills and explore the latest in AI-native
                development.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>The Wisdom Synthesis Engine:</strong> My current project is
                a local-first tool designed to extract high-signal insights from long-form
                YouTube and audio content. To respect data sovereignty and copyright,
                this framework is built to be <strong
                  >downloaded and executed locally</strong
                > for personal research.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Signal over Noise:</strong> The engine automates transcription
                and segmentation, generating structured <strong
                  >PDF summaries</strong
                > and high-fidelity <strong>audio snippets</strong>
                to turn digital content into actionable somatic wisdom.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Sound Engineering:</strong> I continue to offer high-resolution
                audio production for local artists, bringing an engineer's ear to
                every frequency.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div class="clear-both"></div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="fatherhood" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
          <h2
            class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1"
          >
            Parenting & Conscious Leadership
          </h2>

          <div
            class="mt-8 relative text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90 leading-relaxed"
          >
            <div
              class="float-right ml-4 md:ml-10 mb-4 w-28 md:w-36 aspect-square relative group cursor-zoom-in"
            >
              <div
                class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-tr from-amber-200 to-pink-300 rounded-3xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-60 transition duration-700"
              >
              </div>

              <label>
                <input type="checkbox" class="peer hidden" id="zoom-check" />

                <div
                  class="relative h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/40 shadow-xl
                    peer-checked:fixed peer-checked:inset-0 peer-checked:z-50 peer-checked:flex peer-checked:items-center peer-checked:justify-center
                    transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out"
                >
                  <div
                    class="hidden peer-checked:block fixed inset-0 bg-indigo-950/40 backdrop-blur-md cursor-zoom-out"
                  >
                  </div>

                  <Image
                    src={fatherhoodImg}
                    alt="José and his son"
                    class="zoom-target w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-500 peer-checked:relative"
                  />
                </div>
              </label>

              <p
                class="text-[9px] text-center mt-2 text-indigo-900/40 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] group-hover:text-indigo-900/70 transition-colors"
              >
                Click to enlarge
              </p>
            </div>

            <p>
              Navigating a 50/50 co-parenting partnership while managing a
              career pivot is my daily practice. I offer a unique perspective
              for fathers who feel the weight of responsibility and want to lead
              their families with presence rather than pressure.
            </p>

            <p class="mt-5">
              Through this journey, I have learned to <strong
                >self-regulate</strong
              > my nervous system, remain embodied in challenging moments, and engage
              from a genuinely <strong>vulnerable space</strong>. By recognizing
              and healing the connection with my own <strong>inner child</strong
              >, I have found a profound, heart-centered way to connect with my
              son.
            </p>

            <div class="clear-both"></div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <style>
          /* The "Gallery-Scale" Fixed Zoom */
          #zoom-check:checked ~ div .zoom-target {
            /* Mobile: Kept at your perfect size */
            width: 350px !important;
            height: 350px !important;
            border-radius: 2rem !important;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) !important;
          }

          @media (min-width: 768px) {
            #zoom-check:checked ~ div .zoom-target {
              /* Desktop: Increased to 700px for a more powerful focal point */
              width: 700px !important;
              height: 700px !important;
            }
          }
        </style>

        <section id="contact" class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
          <h2
            class="inline-block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-indigo-950/90 border-b border-pink-200 pb-1"
          >
            Work With Me
          </h2>

          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-indigo-900/90">
            <p class="max-w-none">
              I am available for limited 1:1 coaching, sound production, and
              technical collaborations.
            </p>
            <p class="max-w-none">
              Email:
              <a
                href="mailto:joysomatic@gmail.com"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-5 py-2.5 text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-indigo-900/90 bg-violet-200/60 hover:bg-violet-200/90 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(196,181,253,0.7)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
              >
                joysomatic@gmail.com
              </a>
            </p>
            <p class="space-x-3">
              <a
                href="https://linkedin.com/in/joysomatic"
                target="_blank"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 bg-white/70 hover:bg-sky-50 hover:shadow-[0_10px_26px_rgba(59,130,246,0.55)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
              >
                LinkedIn
              </a>
              <span>|</span>
              <a
                href="https://github.com/joysomatic"
                target="_blank"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 bg-white/70 hover:bg-indigo-50 hover:shadow-[0_10px_26px_rgba(129,140,248,0.55)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
              >
                GitHub
              </a>
              <span>|</span>
              <a
                href="https://instagram.com/joysomatic"
                target="_blank"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900/85 bg-white/70 hover:bg-pink-50 hover:shadow-[0_10px_26px_rgba(244,114,182,0.55)] hover:-translate-y-[1px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
              >
                Instagram
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer
        class="mt-16 border-t border-violet-100/80 text-center text-xs md:text-sm text-indigo-900/70 py-6 px-4"
      >
        <p>
          © 2026 JoySomatic – José Oñate Yáñez | Built with Code &amp; Heart
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div></BaseLayout
>
